== DEATH ==
A day before his death on September 16th, 1949 he exposed Enrico Scalice as a rat, but he was not even though he was suspicious and his only friend beated him, and a few hours after that the gang beated him making Nathan suffering bad injuries. On the day of his death on the 17th he was watching a lake, with his two daughters and his wife when one of the gang members stuffed him in a trunk of a car and sank it in the lake, before it sank he screamed for help as they tried saving him, but unfortunaly it was too late he died, the car sank to the bottom of the lake. The funeral was a week after his death and his mother, His two kids and his wife attended, a reporter said to the two kids and the wife, 'How did this happen, you guys were there to see it right." They confirmed and said he drowned in a drunk in a car. A few months after his passing he was convicted even know he was dead for his 3 counts of murderer, and escaping prison multiple times and his other crimes he committed before passing away.
